    <p class="iu__hint label">A reading room in the school of Standard Ebooks: Montaigne at a true 17&nbsp;px, every control live on the column. The figures switch is the spacing truth this file carries — tabular by default, so columns of numbers align; <em>proportional</em> closes up the 1s, visible in the page count. Drag the ink slider and the headline grades with it, the weight value set large in the margin like a compositor&rsquo;s note; the proof line keeps a true <em>frac</em> half, and Night grades the axis up sixty units — ink that glows instead of bites.</p>
